{"tid":2178970,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[小小虫] 是日靚福食 糖醋松子魚","createTime":"2020-08-28T19:13:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T05:58:16.000Z","uid":156466,"like":45,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1f9720033f177de6dfc9ca34e6e1b384989f69fc","tid":2178970,"uid":156466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T19:13:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為有同事釣魚多得濟拎番公司<br />\n所以拎2條細鱗黎整松子魚 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pU98VcL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpU98VcL.png&h=6216b1e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先魚2條打鱗 真正既話要2,3斤大魚好啲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WeNVz9f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWeNVz9f.png&h=451d0dbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n開邊唔好斷魚尾位<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RmH2ZA4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRmH2ZA4.png&h=87a86647&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2邊開柒哂 真係好易斷 盡量唔好開到最尾<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5xE8U9t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5xE8U9t.png&h=287df7a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n改走埋啲腩骨<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ae1vo4w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fae1vo4w.png&h=46920fa5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住打直切唔好穿皮 再45度角橫切<br />\n整啲格仔出黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iojkMhW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiojkMhW.png&h=41a703a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n準備蛋黃 加啲鹽俾啲底味<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Pod6h6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Pod6h6.png&h=75e33c94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n準備一盤生粉<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pNX2ZDb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpNX2ZDb.png&h=70d0affb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n搽撚勻蛋之後 好小心咁上滿生粉<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/16oBjDM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F16oBjDM.png&h=9aa7692f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好小心咁輕手拎住魚尾落去炸 定型先放手<br />\n(唔好介意 換油前黑黑地炸埋唔好sai 唔想開中鍋炸）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LOn2ZDS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLOn2ZDS.png&h=9e1663e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n炸到熟左之後輕力拎出黎 <br />\n一來等油溫升番先脆<br />\n二來整好個醬汁先再最後炸到脆<br />\n(依個moment 仆街喇 唔記得自己改早左5點半開晚市 跟住勁快手埋尾算）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/byY9ED3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbyY9ED3.png&h=7aab5e5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n老豆secret recipe <br />\n趕時間無影 同唔小心整太杰<br />\n<br />\n成份有 <br />\n蒜蓉<br />\n白醋<br />\n茄汁<br />\n糖<br />\n鹽<br />\n生粉水<br />\n有青椒，辣椒更佳<br />\n白醋同茄汁1比1 超酸超正 怕酸加水<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fBUMGSt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfBUMGSt.png&h=274adb4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o754txF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo754txF.png&h=c7729aa1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廢事未食得林哂 個汁onside 算<br />\n結果成班做到11點都未得閒食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pU98VcL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpU98VcL.png&h=6216b1e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係咁"},{"pid":"f931840c43c5b723c1e9a9844f80ec32282f0557","tid":2178970,"uid":174432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T19:14:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4c0284e6b18892d8cd5b2f417cfd537446b3900","tid":2178970,"uid":34544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T19:20:46.000Z","msg":"樓主而家餐廳開係邊"},{"pid":"9100ea7c31df33ad5027be25349c5fe9fa57c936","tid":2178970,"uid":1590,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"e4c0284e6b18892d8cd5b2f417cfd537446b3900","tid":2178970,"uid":34544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T19:20:46.000Z","msg":"樓主而家餐廳開係邊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T19:21:10.000Z","msg":"在你心裡"},{"pid":"2bd6589341f1dab6d644330f71578b9a085f6df7","tid":2178970,"uid":156466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T19:21:41.000Z","msg":"上面唔係我話自己開柒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係唔小心講左粗口咋"},{"pid":"7c471eee010b17a04882e95a399b58474d2a105f","tid":2178970,"uid":156466,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e4c0284e6b18892d8cd5b2f417cfd537446b3900","tid":2178970,"uid":34544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T19:20:46.000Z","msg":"樓主而家餐廳開係邊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T19:22:05.000Z","msg":"九龍塘區"},{"pid":"ba25eb29dc335b4753d794d27db62a6f919a5e00","tid":2178970,"uid":34544,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7c471eee010b17a04882e95a399b58474d2a105f","tid":2178970,"uid":156466,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e4c0284e6b18892d8cd5b2f417cfd537446b3900","tid":2178970,"uid":34544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T19:20:46.000Z","msg":"樓主而家餐廳開係邊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T19:22:05.000Z","msg":"九龍塘區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T19:23:13.000Z","msg":"以前開係荃灣個陣仲讀緊書 略嫌貴<br />\n而家出黎做嘢自己搵錢 想去試下"},{"pid":"484cfcc6133433f40aabace3f1394a4750b34c5a","tid":2178970,"uid":156466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba25eb29dc335b4753d794d27db62a6f919a5e00",